ADDITIONAL NOTICE — TAX-RELATED CONTENT (Brazilian Income Tax)

This Software contains educational content and heuristic tools related to
Brazilian Personal Income Tax (Imposto de Renda Pessoa Física — IRPF). The
author is NOT a certified accountant (contador habilitado) and the content
has NOT been reviewed by a licensed tax professional.

USERS ARE STRONGLY ADVISED to consult a certified Brazilian accountant
(registered at the Conselho Regional de Contabilidade — CRC) or qualified
tax attorney before making any tax-related decisions based on this Software,
particularly for cases involving high income, controlled foreign entities,
real estate transactions, estates, or any situation with significant
financial or patrimonial impact.

The official Brazilian tax filing program ("Programa IRPF") provided by the
Receita Federal do Brasil is the only authoritative tool for income tax
declaration. This Software does NOT replace, substitute, or interface with
the official program for transmission of tax returns.

See DISCLAIMER.md for full details.
